{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":603,"text":"Do you remember\nthese glow-in-the-dark little stars"},{"time":3177,"text":"which you had on the ceiling\nwhen you were a boy or a girl?"},{"time":6091,"text":"Yes?"},{"time":7325,"text":"It is light."},{"time":8545,"text":"It is pure light."},{"time":9753,"text":"I think I stared at them way too long"},{"time":11679,"text":"when I was a five-year-old, you know?"},{"time":13476,"text":"It's so beautiful:"},{"time":14724,"text":"no energy bill, no maintenance."},{"time":17505,"text":"It is there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18733,"text":"So two years ago, we went back to the lab,"},{"time":20814,"text":"making it more durable,\nmore light-emitting,"},{"time":23136,"text":"with the experts."},{"time":24540,"text":"And at the same time,\nwe got a request from this guy --"},{"time":28245,"text":"Van Gogh, the famous\nVan Gogh Foundation --"},{"time":30847,"text":"who wanted to celebrate\nhis 125th anniversary in the Netherlands."},{"time":35232,"text":"And they came to me and asked,"},{"time":37121,"text":"\"Can you make a place\nwhere he feels more alive again"},{"time":40946,"text":"in the Netherlands?\""},{"time":42176,"text":"And I liked that question a lot,"},{"time":43754,"text":"so in way,"},{"time":44932,"text":"we sort of started to connect\nthese two different worlds."},{"time":49027,"text":"This is how my brain works,"},{"time":50348,"text":"by the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51522,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":52597,"text":"I would love to keep on\ndoing this for an hour,"},{"time":54832,"text":"but OK --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":56007,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57039,"text":"And this is the result that we made:"},{"time":58841,"text":"a bicycle path which charges\nat daytime via the sun"},{"time":61587,"text":"and glows at night, up to eight hours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63733,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64985,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66335,"text":"... hinting towards a future\nwhich should be energy friendly"},{"time":70726,"text":"and linking up the local grounds"},{"time":72446,"text":"as Van Gogh literally walked\nand lived there in 1883."},{"time":75897,"text":"And you can go there every night\nfor free, no ticket needed."},{"time":79228,"text":"People experience the beauty\nof cycling through the starry night,"},{"time":82458,"text":"thinking about green energy and safety."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84507,"text":"I want to create places\nwhere people feel connected again."},{"time":88766,"text":"And it was somehow great\nto make these projects happen"},{"time":91878,"text":"with the industry,\nwith the infrastructure companies."},{"time":94748,"text":"So when these sheikhs of Qatar\nstarted to call:"},{"time":97061,"text":"\"How much for 10 kilometers?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":98586,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":99625,"text":"Yeah, really, that's a weird call\nyou're going to get."},{"time":102361,"text":"But it's fascinating"},{"time":103545,"text":"that this is not just a sort\nof one-off, nice-to-have special."},{"time":106977,"text":"I think this kind of creative thinking,\nthese kinds of connections --"},{"time":110424,"text":"it's the new economy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111632,"text":"The World Economic Forum,\nthe think tank in Geneva,"},{"time":114403,"text":"did an interview\nwith a lot of smart people"},{"time":116826,"text":"all around the world,"},{"time":118006,"text":"asking, \"What are the top 10 skills\nyou and I need to become successful?\""},{"time":122852,"text":"And what is interesting,\nwhat you see here:"},{"time":125196,"text":"it's not about money"},{"time":127759,"text":"or being really good in C++,"},{"time":130684,"text":"although these are great skills\nto have, I have to admit."},{"time":133725,"text":"But look at number three, creativity;"},{"time":136105,"text":"number two, critical thinking;"},{"time":138341,"text":"number one, complex problem-solving --"},{"time":141465,"text":"all the things a robot or a computer\nis really bad at."},{"time":146662,"text":"And this makes me very optimistic,\nvery hopeful for the new world,"},{"time":150339,"text":"that as we will live\nin this hyper-technological world,"},{"time":153239,"text":"our human skills --"},{"time":154705,"text":"our desire for empathy,"},{"time":156073,"text":"our desire for curiosity,"},{"time":158363,"text":"our desire for beauty --"},{"time":160102,"text":"will be more appreciated again,"},{"time":161860,"text":"and we will live in a world\nwhere creativity is our true capital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166784,"text":"And a creative process like that --"},{"time":169267,"text":"I don't know how it works for you,"},{"time":170990,"text":"but in my brain, it always starts\nwith a question:"},{"time":173705,"text":"Why?"},{"time":175884,"text":"Why does a jellyfish emit light?"},{"time":178431,"text":"Or a firefly?"},{"time":179810,"text":"Or why do be accept pollution?"},{"time":182080,"text":"This is from my room\nin Beijing three years ago."},{"time":184353,"text":"Left image is a good day -- Saturday."},{"time":186521,"text":"I can see the cars\nand the people, the birds;"},{"time":188766,"text":"life is OK in a dense urban city."},{"time":191382,"text":"And on the right image --"},{"time":193238,"text":"holy moly."},{"time":195062,"text":"Pollution -- complete layers."},{"time":197099,"text":"I couldn't even see\nthe other side of the city."},{"time":199831,"text":"And this image made me really sad."},{"time":201691,"text":"This is not the bright future\nwe envision here at TED --"},{"time":204764,"text":"this is the horror."},{"time":205961,"text":"We live five to six years shorter;"},{"time":207736,"text":"children have lung cancer\nwhen they're six years old."},{"time":210828,"text":"And so in a weird, beautiful way,"},{"time":213338,"text":"I, at that moment, became inspired\nby Beijing smog."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217849,"text":"And the governments all around the world\nare fighting their war on smog,"},{"time":221356,"text":"but I wanted to make something\nwithin the now."},{"time":224018,"text":"So we decided to build\nthe largest smog vacuum cleaner"},{"time":227840,"text":"in the world."},{"time":229275,"text":"It sucks up polluted air, cleans it"},{"time":231248,"text":"and then releases it."},{"time":232696,"text":"And we built the first one."},{"time":234865,"text":"So it sucks up 30,000\ncubic meters per hour,"},{"time":237526,"text":"cleans it on the nano level --\nthe PM2.5, PM10 particles --"},{"time":241337,"text":"using very little electricity,"},{"time":243336,"text":"and then releases the clean air,"},{"time":245827,"text":"so we have parks, playgrounds,\nwhich are 55 to 75 percent more clean"},{"time":251304,"text":"than the rest of the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252895,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":254588,"text":"Yes!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":256040,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":257581,"text":"And every month or so,"},{"time":260502,"text":"it opens like a spaceship --"},{"time":264417,"text":"like a Marilyn Monroe with the --\nwell, you know what."},{"time":267100,"text":"Anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268314,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":269414,"text":"So this ..."},{"time":270888,"text":"this is the stuff we are capturing."},{"time":273310,"text":"This is Beijing smog."},{"time":275760,"text":"This is in our lungs right now."},{"time":277402,"text":"If you live next to a highway,\nit's the same as 17 cigarettes per day."},{"time":280848,"text":"Are we insane?"},{"time":282022,"text":"When did we say yes to that?"},{"time":284028,"text":"And we had buckets\nof this disgusting material"},{"time":287295,"text":"in our studio,"},{"time":288863,"text":"and on a Monday morning,\nwe were discussing, we were like,"},{"time":291696,"text":"\"Shit, what should we do with it?\nShould we throw it away?\""},{"time":294570,"text":"Like, \"Help!\""},{"time":295749,"text":"And then we realized:\nno, no, no, no, no --"},{"time":297934,"text":"waste should not exist."},{"time":299150,"text":"Waste for the one should be\nfood for the other."},{"time":302350,"text":"So, here, maybe show it around."},{"time":304870,"text":"Do not put this in your coffee."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306457,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":307492,"text":"And we realized that 42 percent\nis made out of carbon,"},{"time":310527,"text":"and carbon, of course,\nunder high pressure,"},{"time":312719,"text":"you get ..."},{"time":314871,"text":"diamonds."},{"time":316299,"text":"So, inspired by that,\nwe compress it for 30 minutes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":320454,"text":"(Cracking sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":321565,"text":"and make smog-free rings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323669,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":324716,"text":"And so by sharing -- yeah, really!"},{"time":326716,"text":"And so by sharing a ring,"},{"time":328378,"text":"you donate 1,000 cubic meters of clean air"},{"time":331008,"text":"to the city the tower is in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332697,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333733,"text":"I have one here --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":334987,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336191,"text":"A little floating cube."},{"time":340163,"text":"I will give one to you."},{"time":341337,"text":"I'm not going to propose, don't worry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343591,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":344903,"text":"Are we good?"},{"time":346092,"text":"You can show it around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347358,"text":"And we put this online --\nKickstarter campaign, crowdfunding."},{"time":350792,"text":"And people started to preorder it,"},{"time":352605,"text":"but more importantly,\nthey started to prepay it."},{"time":355459,"text":"So the finance we made with the jewelry\nhelped us to realize,"},{"time":358852,"text":"to build the first tower."},{"time":360873,"text":"And that's powerful."},{"time":362047,"text":"So the waste the activator,\nit was the enabler."},{"time":364708,"text":"Also, the feedback from the community --"},{"time":366742,"text":"this is a wedding couple from India,"},{"time":368582,"text":"where he proposed to her\nwith the smog-free ring"},{"time":371067,"text":"as a sign of true beauty,"},{"time":372364,"text":"as a sign of hope."},{"time":374257,"text":"And she said yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376119,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":377858,"text":"I love this image so much\nfor a lot of different reasons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381365,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382616,"text":"And right now, the project\nis touring through China,"},{"time":385335,"text":"actually with the support\nof China's central government."},{"time":388231,"text":"So the first goal is to create\nlocal clean-air parks,"},{"time":391348,"text":"and that works already quite well --"},{"time":393372,"text":"55, 75 percent more clean."},{"time":395656,"text":"And at the same time,"},{"time":397029,"text":"we team up with the NGOs,"},{"time":398450,"text":"with the governors,"},{"time":399638,"text":"with the students,"},{"time":400862,"text":"with the tech people,"},{"time":402037,"text":"to say, \"Hey, what do we need to do\nto make a whole city smog-free?\""},{"time":405416,"text":"It's about the dream of clean air."},{"time":407223,"text":"We do workshops. New ideas pop up."},{"time":409493,"text":"These are smog-free bicycles\nwhich -- I'm Dutch, yes? --"},{"time":412311,"text":"I have this \"bicycle DNA\"\ninside of me somewhere."},{"time":414774,"text":"And so it sucks up polluted air,"},{"time":416448,"text":"it cleans it and releases it,"},{"time":418031,"text":"in the fight against the car,"},{"time":419548,"text":"in the celebration of the bicycle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421453,"text":"And so right now, we're working\non a sort of \"package deal,\" so to speak,"},{"time":425638,"text":"where we say, \"Smog-free towers,\nsmog-free rings.\""},{"time":428916,"text":"We go to the mayors\nor the governors of this world,"},{"time":431436,"text":"and say, \"We can guarantee\na short-term reduction of pollution"},{"time":435563,"text":"between 20 and 40 percent."},{"time":437670,"text":"Please sign here right now.\""},{"time":439591,"text":"Yes?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440766,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442517,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443691,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445545,"text":"So it's all about connecting\nnew technology with creative thinking."},{"time":450496,"text":"And if you start thinking about that,"},{"time":452462,"text":"there is so much you can imagine,"},{"time":454647,"text":"so much more you can do."},{"time":456194,"text":"We worked on dance floors\nwhich produce electricity"},{"time":459529,"text":"when you dance on them."},{"time":460812,"text":"We did the design for that -- 2008."},{"time":463314,"text":"So it moves eight or nine millimeters,"},{"time":465333,"text":"produces 25 watts."},{"time":467035,"text":"The electricity that we generate\nis used for the lighting or the DJ booth."},{"time":471056,"text":"So some of the sustainability\nis about doing more,"},{"time":473744,"text":"not about doing less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475431,"text":"But also on a larger scale,"},{"time":476941,"text":"the Netherlands, where I'm\nfrom, we live below sea level."},{"time":480414,"text":"So because of these beauties --"},{"time":482716,"text":"the Afsluitdijk: 32 kilometers,\nbuilt by hand in 1932 --"},{"time":488180,"text":"we live with the water,"},{"time":489971,"text":"we fight with the water,"},{"time":491525,"text":"we try to find harmony,"},{"time":493695,"text":"but sometimes we forget."},{"time":496163,"text":"And therefore, we made \"Waterlicht,\""},{"time":498130,"text":"a combination of LEDs and lenses,"},{"time":500374,"text":"which show how high\nthe water level would be --"},{"time":503012,"text":"global change --"},{"time":504859,"text":"if we stop."},{"time":506408,"text":"If, today, we all go home and we say,"},{"time":509133,"text":"\"Oh, whatever, somebody else\nwill do it for us,\""},{"time":511578,"text":"or we'll wait for government or whomever."},{"time":513622,"text":"You know, we're not going to do that."},{"time":515512,"text":"It goes wrong."},{"time":516695,"text":"And we placed this in public spaces\nall around the world."},{"time":519435,"text":"Thousands of people showed up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521050,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":522322,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":524117,"text":"You're too nice, you're too nice.\nThat's not good for a designer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527702,"text":"So thousands of people showed up,"},{"time":529726,"text":"and some, actually, were scared."},{"time":531520,"text":"And they left; they experienced\nthe floods in 1953."},{"time":534885,"text":"And others were mesmerized."},{"time":536301,"text":"Can we make floating cities?"},{"time":538144,"text":"Can we generate electricity\nfrom the change in tides?"},{"time":542044,"text":"So I think it's so important\nto make experiences --"},{"time":545019,"text":"collective experiences --"},{"time":546577,"text":"where people feel connected\nwith a vision, with a future"},{"time":550255,"text":"and trigger what is possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552822,"text":"At the same time,"},{"time":554216,"text":"you know, these kinds of things --\nthey're not easy, yes?"},{"time":558734,"text":"It's a struggle."},{"time":560012,"text":"And what I experienced in my life"},{"time":561702,"text":"is that a lot of people say\nthey want innovation,"},{"time":564125,"text":"and they want the next\nand the new, the future."},{"time":566747,"text":"But the moment you present a new idea,"},{"time":569808,"text":"there's this weird tendency\nto reply to every new idea"},{"time":574218,"text":"starting with two words."},{"time":577468,"text":"Which are?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":578674,"text":"(Audience guesses)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":580044,"text":"No, not \"How much?\" It's more annoying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582250,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583282,"text":"What is it, guys?"},{"time":584459,"text":"Or you're really blessed people?\nThat's really good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":587024,"text":"\"Yes, but.\" Very good."},{"time":588244,"text":"\"Yes, but: it's too expensive, it's too\ncheap, it's too fast, it's too slow,"},{"time":591960,"text":"it's too beautiful, it's too ugly,\nit cannot be done, it already exists.\""},{"time":595467,"text":"I heard everything about the same project"},{"time":597578,"text":"in the same week."},{"time":598762,"text":"And I got really, really annoyed."},{"time":600715,"text":"I got a bit of gray hair, started to dress\nin black like a true architect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604977,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":607449,"text":"And one morning I woke up\nand I said, \"Daan, stop."},{"time":610931,"text":"This is dragging you down."},{"time":612306,"text":"You have to do something with this."},{"time":614085,"text":"You have to use it\nas an ingredient, as a component.\""},{"time":616804,"text":"And so we decided to build,"},{"time":618793,"text":"to realize the famous \"Yes, but\" chair."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":626461,"text":"And this is an existing chair\nby Friso Kramer, a Dutch design."},{"time":629839,"text":"But we gave it a little \"update,\""},{"time":632647,"text":"a little \"hack,\" so to speak."},{"time":635002,"text":"We placed a little voice-recognition\nelement right here."},{"time":639100,"text":"So the moment you sit on that chair,"},{"time":641921,"text":"and you say those two horrible,"},{"time":645231,"text":"creative-destructive,\nannoying little words --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":649705,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":650820,"text":"you get a short --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":652499,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":654146,"text":"but pretty intense"},{"time":655743,"text":"little shock on the back side\nof your bottom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658582,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":659763,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":661176,"text":"And --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":662371,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":663423,"text":"and that works; yeah, that works."},{"time":665245,"text":"Some clients have left us,\nthey got really mad."},{"time":668044,"text":"Fortunately, the good ones have stayed."},{"time":670049,"text":"And, of course, we also\napply it to ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":672460,"text":"But ladies and gentlemen,\nlet's not be afraid."},{"time":675630,"text":"Let's be curious, yes?"},{"time":677425,"text":"And, you know, walking\nthrough TED in these days"},{"time":679967,"text":"and hearing the other speakers"},{"time":681690,"text":"and feeling the energy of the crowd,"},{"time":684134,"text":"I was remembering this quote\nof the Canadian author, Marshall McLuhan,"},{"time":688457,"text":"who once famously said,"},{"time":690496,"text":"\"On spacecraft earth,"},{"time":692399,"text":"there are no passengers."},{"time":693939,"text":"We are all crew.\""},{"time":697026,"text":"And I think this so beautiful."},{"time":699268,"text":"This is so beautiful!"},{"time":700744,"text":"We're not just consumers; we're makers:"},{"time":703014,"text":"we make decisions,"},{"time":704244,"text":"we make new inventions,"},{"time":705439,"text":"we make new dreams."},{"time":707076,"text":"And I think"},{"time":708261,"text":"if we start implementing\nthat kind of thinking even more"},{"time":712350,"text":"within today,"},{"time":714551,"text":"there's still a whole new world\nto be explored."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718545,"text":"All right, thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720003,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":722155,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723329,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}